<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c5">ورجلٌ مِسْدَع:</span> ماضٍ لوجهه.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
